OL,3,CCCTV released following #2000 worth of
OL,4,Ctools stolen from Hampshire school
OL,6,FOfficers investigating a burglary at a
OL,7,Fschool in Petersfield are appealing
OL,8,Ffor witnesses and releasing CCTV
OL,9,Fimages.
OL,11,FIt was reported that between 11.50pm
OL,12,Fon Monday 20 April and 12.20am on
OL,13,FTuesday 21 April, two unknown
OL,14,Findividuals broke into sheds at
OL,15,FChurcher's College, stealing over
OL,16,F#2,000 worth of tools.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
