OL,3,CCCTV released following #2000 worth of
OL,4,Ctools stolen from Hampshire school
OL,6,FBoth individuals were described as
OL,7,Fwearing hooded jackets and tracksuit
OL,8,Fbottoms. One of the tracksuits had a
OL,9,Fdistinct dark stripe down the leg, and
OL,10,Fthe second had a reflective stripe.
OL,12,FOfficers have carried out several
OL,13,Fenquiries and are now releasing CCTV
OL,14,Fimages and asking the public for any
OL,15,Finformation that may help the
OL,16,Finvestigation.
